GK19uddkokiu:503: vāmaṃ netraṃ sphurati sucirāducchvasityadya cetaḥ Kok_2.42b
GK19uddkokiu:505: vāmotsaṅge lasati karuṇā kāpi kāmaṃ duhānā Kok_1.28d
GK19uddkokiu:506: vāmo bāhustvayi savidhage yāsyati spandamasyāḥ Kok_2.44d
GK19uddkokiu:512: viśrāntaḥ san kvacana vipule vṛkṣaśākhākuṭumbe Kok_1.57c
GK19uddkokiu:514: viśleṣe tu tribhuvanamidaṃ jāyate tvanmayaṃ hi Kok_2.67d
GK19uddkokiu:517: vīcīgarvaṃ harati nikhilaṃ vibhramāndolitā bhrūḥ Kok_2.22b
GK19uddkokiu:528: vyarthaṃ karṇe navakuvalayaṃ vidyamāne kaṭākṣe Kok_1.66a
GK19uddkokiu:533: śaśvadyasmin kimapi valati smāvayoḥ premavallī Kok_2.16d
GK19uddkokiu:534: śaṃsanti tvāṃ nanu parabhṛtaṃ śaiśave yadbhṛto 'nyaiḥ Kok_2.68c
GK19uddkokiu:535: śāstā tasyā yadi taṭapathaiḥ śambarakroḍavāsī Kok_1.75a
GK19uddkokiu:537: śuśrāvetthaṃ sa punaravapussaṅgrahāṃ vyomni vāṇīm Kok_1.2d
GK19uddkokiu:538: śūnyāśleṣaṃ viracitavatī hanta ghātāt kucādryoḥ Kok_2.41b
GK19uddkokiu:540: śṛṅgārābdhiplava iva galadveṇi kamprastanaṃ tat Kok_2.9a
GK19uddkokiu:541: śṛṅgārābdheḥ śaśadharakalā jīvitaṃ me dvitīyam Kok_2.19d
GK19uddkokiu:543: śṛṅge śṛṅge gṛhaviṭapināṃ spaṣṭayiṣyanti kīrāḥ Kok_1.26d
GK19uddkokiu:548: śyāmā varṇe vacasi madhurā cañcalā dṛgvilāse Kok_1.28c
GK19uddkokiu:552: śroṇībimbe sumahati tayā bhūṣite komalāṅgyāḥ Kok_2.30c
GK19uddkokiu:554: śroṇyāṃ kṣaumaṃ malinamasṛṇaṃ sā vahatyeva hantety Kok_2.34c
GK19uddkokiu:556: śvetāraṇyaṃ vraja bahumataṃ dhāma mṛtyuñjayasya Kok_1.70b
GK19uddkokiu:558: saṅkocaṃ me vrajati rasanā sandidikṣormṛgākṣyāḥ Kok_1.9b
GK19uddkokiu:561: satyaṃ taistaiḥ kṛtadhṛtirahaṃ prāṇimi prāṇanāthe Kok_2.60b
GK19uddkokiu:562: satyaṃ prāṇānapi paramahaṃ tvatpriyān dhārayāmi Kok_2.56d
GK19uddkokiu:564: santāpārtāṃ suvacana samāśvāsaya preyasīṃ me Kok_1.10b
GK19uddkokiu:566: sandigdhāyāṃ vipadi sahasāvṛttirārtiṃ hi sūte Kok_1.40d
GK19uddkokiu:567: sandeśaṃ me naya khagapate sādhaya bhrātṛkṛtyaṃ Kok_1.10a
GK19uddkokiu:569: sabhrūcāpaṃ nayanajaladaṃ prāpya yasyāḥ kṛpāpaṃ Kok_1.17c
GK19uddkokiu:570: sampadgrāmaṃ yadi na bhajase janmanā kiṃ bhṛtena Kok_1.50d
GK19uddkokiu:571: sampanmūrtiṃ praṇama girijāṃ sā hi viśvasya mātā Kok_1.85d
GK19uddkokiu:573: sambhogānte muhurapi mayā sādaraṃ cumbito yaḥ Kok_2.28b
GK19uddkokiu:574: sambhogānte svapanavidhaye yaḥ purā dhūyate sma Kok_2.44b
GK19uddkokiu:576: sarvaṃ caitanmadanaghaṭitaṃ saumya sambhūya sābhūt Kok_2.21d
GK19uddkokiu:577: sarvotkṛṣṭā jagati viditāḥ keraleṣu dvijendrā Kok_1.76a
GK19uddkokiu:581: saṃskartāsi dhruvamupagato yatra patrīndra teṣām Kok_1.13c
GK19uddkokiu:582: sākaṃ kāntairmilati lalitaṃ keralīnāṃ kadambe Kok_1.73a
GK19uddkokiu:584: sā kāntiśceddravati kanakaṃ tanmukhaṃ cet ka induḥ Kok_2.23a
GK19uddkokiu:586: sā ca prekṣyā saridanupadaṃ yatra kalmāṣitāyāṃ Kok_1.89a
GK19uddkokiu:587: sācīkṛtya sphuradadharayā caṇḍi vaktraṃ bhavatyā Kok_2.63c
GK19uddkokiu:588: sā ced bimbādharamadhuratā tiktatāmeti mādhvī Kok_2.23b
GK19uddkokiu:592: sāndrāmodaṃ sapaṭu sadayaṃ sasmaraṃ sānutarṣaṃ Kok_2.28a
GK19uddkokiu:593: sāraṅgākṣi spṛhayati mano hanta cakrākhyayūne Kok_2.55d
GK19uddkokiu:594: sālāvītāṃ sa kila madano manyate rājadhānīm Kok_2.30d
GK19uddkokiu:595: sā vā tasyā yadi tanulatā mālatī lohatulyā Kok_2.23c
GK19uddkokiu:596: sā vaidagdhī śrutiṣu sa punaḥ sarvaśāstrāvagāhas Kok_1.26a
GK19uddkokiu:598: siktaḥ svacchairjharajalakaṇaistaṃ bhaja vyomni tiṣṭhan Kok_1.43a
GK19uddkokiu:601: sītkurvāṇāṃ dhutakaratalāṃ tvāṃ priye smārayanti Kok_2.53d
GK19uddkokiu:605: seyaṃ mattaḥ śravaṇasarasā śrūyatāṃ śrāvyabandhā Kok_2.49d
GK19uddkokiu:608: seviṣyante niśi parabhṛta tvāṃ sukhena prasuptam Kok_1.58d
GK19uddkokiu:613: so 'yaṃ bhedo viṣayabhidayā saṅgame tvaṃ kilaikā Kok_2.67c
GK19uddkokiu:614: saudhe tuṅge saha dayitayā ko 'pi saṅkrīḍamānaḥ Kok_1.1a
GK19uddkokiu:615: saudhe saudhe surabhikusumaiḥ kalpitaṃ kelitalpam Kok_1.65b
GK19uddkokiu:620: strīṇāṃ ceṣṭāsviti hi virahotthāsu diṅmātrametat Kok_2.43d
GK19uddkokiu:625: snānānte te mukhamupasakhi prekṣamāṇe mayi drāg- Kok_2.62c
GK19uddkokiu:630: spṛśyete nau niśi śaśikarairaṅgake yaugapadyāt Kok_2.57c
GK19uddkokiu:631: smāraṃ smāraṃ kathamapi mayā muhyatā sahyate 'sau Kok_2.54c
GK19uddkokiu:632: smāraṃ smāraṃ dviguṇagamanotsāha eva dhruvaṃ syāḥ Kok_1.60d
GK19uddkokiu:633: smitvā ramyaṃ sakalamiti vā cittamāśvāsayantī Kok_2.36d
GK19uddkokiu:636: svātī nāma kṣitipatisutā sevituṃ devamasyāḥ Kok_1.47c
GK19uddkokiu:641: svairālāpaistava pika girāṃ kāpi śikṣā bhavitrī Kok_1.47d
GK19uddkokiu:642: harmye yasyāṃ hariṇanayanāḥ kurvate 'smin kalaṅkaṃ Kok_2.2c
GK19uddkokiu:643: haste kṛtvā kathamapi śanairaśmapṛṣṭhe nyadhāyi Kok_1.78b
GK19uddkokiu:647: haimīṃ lekhāmapi tu janayatyeva varṇaprakarṣam Kok_2.33d
